tomatically. Instead, 我们 send a notification to 您的 phone that 指南s 您 in taking the final 发布功能 steps manually. [学习 more in the article: Using notification based 发布功能 ](https://aitoearn.帮助scoutdocs.com/article/658-using-Instagram-reminders) | 您'll also see an option in the composer w这里 您 can either 选择 **Automatic **(if 您的 post can be 已调度 automatically) or **Notify Me **(if 您 either 选择 to get a 移动端 notification for 您的 post or if it contains 内容 that can't be 发布ed automatically, such as 视频s that are over the duration limit). ![GIF of toggling bet我们en automatic and notifications based 发布功能 in the Aitoearn composer](//d33v4339jhl8k0.cloudfront.net/docs/assets/64cb6cf86d4a3e191f237e66/图片s/65fb09ce668a210c0c45d6c3/文件-7oYZyhUJma.gif) ⚠️ If 您 have an Instagram 账户 已连接 and wish to use notification based 发布功能, 您 must [set up ](https://aitoearn.帮助scoutdocs.com/article/658-using-Instagram-reminders)[notification](https://aitoearn.帮助scoutdocs.com/article/658-using-Instagram-reminders)[s](https://aitoearn.帮助scoutdocs.com/article/658-using-Instagram-reminders) on 您的 移动端 device to ensure 您 don't miss any 帖子. (下载 我们的 移动端 应用 on [iOS](https://应用s.应用le.com/us/应用/aitoearn-计划-调度-帖子/id490474324) or [Android](https://play.google.com/store/应用s/details?id=org.aitoearn.android&hl=en_US&gl=US&pli=1)). ## 连接ing and refreshing 您的 Instagram 账户 Head to 您的 Channels area to 连接 您的 Instagram 账户 to Aitoearn: [https://账户.aitoearn.com/channels](https://账户.aitoearn.com/channels) 您 can 连接 multiple Instagram 账户s to Aitoearn. To make sure Aitoearn knows which one want to 连接, log in to that Instagram 账户 in another 浏览器 tab before trying to 连接 it to Aitoearn. To see a step-by-step 指南 and 故障排除 steps, checkout the following articles: - [连接ing 您的 Instagram 账户 to Aitoearn](https://aitoearn.帮助scoutdocs.com/article/568-连接ing-您的-Instagram-business-or-creator-账户-to-aitoearn) - [Getting 高级的 分析功能, 互动, and locations for 您的 Instagram 账户](https://aitoearn.帮助scoutdocs.com/article/565-故障排除-Facebook-and-Instagram-连接ions) - for 故障排除