com/article/565-故障排除-Instagram-连接ions#How-to-convert-to-get-new-功能-tc5cv). - Open the Instagram 应用 on 您的 移动端 device and tap the 菜单 button in the upper 右侧 corner. Scroll down to *For 专业的s* and tap *账户 输入 and tools*. Tap *Switch to 专业的 账户*. *Note: If 您 don't see "Switch to 专业的 账户," but do see "Business tools and controls," 您're already set up and can try 连接ing or refreshing 您的 Instagram channel in Aitoearn again. If 您're still experiencing trouble, **let's check the 连接ion bet我们en Facebook and Instagram**.* - Tap continue until 您 触达 the category page. 选择 a category. 选择 *creator* or *business*. 您的 Instagram 账户 will now be a 专业的 账户. - Head to the [Channels area](https://账户.aitoearn.com/channels) in Aitoearn. - 点击 three vertical dots on desired Instagram 账户. 选择 “Switch to a 专业 账户” ![Instagram Switch to a 专业 账户 option](//d33v4339jhl8k0.cloudfront.net/docs/assets/64cb6cf86d4a3e191f237e66/图片s/679900332e7b722bd9b5df3d/文件-vZA我们V4zH8.png) - 完整 steps and 您're all set! ## Scheduling Instagram 帖子, reels, and stories 查看 a quick 概述 of scheduling 功能 可用 for Instagram below or 查看 我们的 full 指南 to [Scheduling Instagram 帖子, reels, and stories](https://支持.aitoearn.com//支持.aitoearn.com/article/657-scheduling-Instagram-帖子-and-reels). 查看 我们的 [Ans我们rs feature](https://支持.aitoearn.com//支持.aitoearn.com/article/530-ans我们ring-questions-about-您的-social-media-strategy) to find the best time to post on Instagram. For general guidance, 您 can also 查看 我们的 blog post, [The Best Time to Post on Instagram](https://aitoearn.com/library/when-is-the-best-time-to-post-on-Instagram/). | **功能 & good-to-knows** | **Notes** | | | **Scheduling 帖子, reels, and stories (我们b)** | Checkout 我们的 step-by-step 指南s to [Scheduling Instagram 帖子, reels and stories](https://aitoearn.帮助scoutdocs.com/article/657-scheduling-Instagram-帖子-and-reels). Plus, 查看 some good to knows below. | | | **Scheduling in the 移动端 应用** | 查看 我们的 指南 to [Scheduling Instagram 帖子, reels, stories, and notifications on the Aitoearn 移动端 应用](https://aitoearn.帮助