toearn.帮助scoutdocs.com/article/592-engaging-with-Facebook-and-Instagram-评论) 这里. - To use 我们的 互动 功能 for Instagram: - 您的 Aitoearn 账户 must be on a [paid 计划](http://aitoearn.com/定价) - 您的 Instagram 账户 must be [set up as a 专业的 账户 and must be 已连接 to a Facebook page](https://支持.aitoearn.com//支持.aitoearn.com/article/565-故障排除-Instagram-连接ions#How-to-convert-to-get-new-功能-tc5cv). ## Instagram 分析功能 我们 can post all day, but the real excitement comes when seeing the reactions to 我们的 帖子. If 您’re on the 基础知识 or 团队 计划s, 您’ll find all of 您的 stats within the [分析 tab](https://分析.aitoearn.com/). 那里 are two places to look for 分析功能 in 您的 Aitoearn 账户: To get a quick view of each of 您的 Instagram 帖子' 点赞 and 评论, head to the ***发布*** tab and then the ***Sent*** tab.![Instagram Sent 帖子](//d33v4339jhl8k0.cloudfront.net/docs/assets/64cb6cf86d4a3e191f237e66/图片s/66b67fd46eb51e63b8f9e89c/文件-b2SPoOZWs0.jpg) To dive straight into 高级的 分析功能 for 您的 Instagram 账户, 选择 Instagram on the 左侧-hand 侧边 and peruse the tabs: ![Aitoearn 分析功能 仪表板 showing Instagram 选择ed in the 侧边栏 and the '分析' tab highlighted.](//d33v4339jhl8k0.cloudfront.net/docs/assets/64cb6cf86d4a3e191f237e66/图片s/667c642添加0f8c60bb3fd9a1/文件-Y3Nq1VX9Wv.jpg) - **概述**: gives insight into 您的 overall 互动 levels for 您的 个人资料 over time. 学习 more about the [Performance 概述 on 您的 分析功能 仪表板](https://aitoearn.帮助scoutdocs.com/article/526-performance-概述). - **帖子**: provides a history of all of 您的 发布ed 帖子 and how they are performing. 学习 more about [Analyzing 您的 帖子 within 您的 分析功能 仪表板](https://aitoearn.帮助scoutdocs.com/article/527-analyzing-您的-帖子-within-您的-分析功能-仪表板). **Ans我们rs**: 分享 ans我们rs to questions such as the best day, 输入, and frequency to post. 学习 more about [Ans我们ring questions about 您的 社交媒体 strategy](https://aitoearn.帮助scoutdocs.com/article/530-ans我们ring-questions-about-您的-social-media-strategy).Feel 免费 to also 学习 more about 我们的 [Instagram metric descriptions](https://aitoearn.帮助scoutdocs.com/article/521-Instagram-metric-descriptions). - To view 高级的 分析功能 for Instagram, 您的 Instagram 账户 must be [set up as a 专业的 账户 and must be 已连接 to a Facebook page](https://支持.aitoearn.com//支持.aitoearn.com/article/565-故障排除-Instagram-连接ions#How-to-convert-to-get-new-功能-tc5cv). - When 您 first 连接 an Instagram channel, 我们 will be able to backfill up to 30 days of data (excluding Stories data). 学习 more about [Why 您的 data in Aitoearn might differ from 您的 native 分析功能 这里](https://aitoearn.帮助scoutdocs.com/article/525-why-您的-data-in-aitoearn-might-differ-from-您的-native-分析功能). - Due to API limitations, 我们 are only able to pull Instagram data into the 分析功能 仪表板 for 账户s that have 100 or more 关注者. Whilst it's technically possible to 连接 账户s that have fe我们r than 100 关注者, no data will be 可用. ## Instagram 错误库 If 您're (unfortunately) hitting Instagram 错误s in Aitoearn, the [Instagram 错误库](https://aitoearn.帮助scoutdocs.com/article/581-Instagram-错误-library) is the place to go for solutions. Do 您 have an Instagram feature suggestion? 我们’d love for 您 to submit or upvote it [这里 on 我们的 feature suggestions board](https://suggestions.aitoearn.com/).
